{"tid":2285954,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子紅磡海濱墮海 送院搶救","createTime":"2020-11-14T14:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T19:28:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e58c7fa87f731aab73389b975238ed0f391e2063","tid":2285954,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:18:34.000Z","msg":"晚上8時許，一名30多歲男子在紅磡海逸豪園對開海濱長廊墮海，附近經過街坊目擊情況後大驚報警。男子其後被救回岸邊但昏迷，並由救護車送伊利沙伯醫院搶救，目前情況未明，男子身份和墮海原因仍待了解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201114/Q64OIBM6D5GEDDW7CTY4KSCELU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201114%2FQ64OIBM6D5GEDDW7CTY4KSCELU%2F&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=3bc4d84e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201114%2FQ64OIBM6D5GEDDW7CTY4KSCELU%2F&h=bcf22b58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201114/Q64OIBM6D5GEDDW7CTY4KSCELU/</a>"},{"pid":"6c05bfec1edc8abff26d8c634806356a77baac18","tid":2285954,"uid":362346,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:20:37.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae7056bfb9ab0f922db4a1a590519012cc1653d","tid":2285954,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c05bfec1edc8abff26d8c634806356a77baac18","tid":2285954,"uid":362346,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:20:37.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:21:19.000Z","msg":"你又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eaba832bf5bfc0b657385d33d16dc9c4a37fac1","tid":2285954,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:22:02.000Z","